Introduction

Honey J is a South Korean singer, dancer and choreographer under MORE VISION. She is the leader of the dance crew HolyBang. In 2021, she became a participant in the survival show Street Woman Fighter. HolyBang became the winners of Street Woman Fighter 2021. She was part of the dance crew PURPLOW from 2011 through 2017 and a choreographer and dancer for Jay Park and AOMG artists. She made her debut on August 28, 2022, with the single "Honey Drop" featuring Lil Cherry.
